# Environment variables for thesis-agents-python.
# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in real values. config.py reads these
# with safe defaults; required secrets have NO default and fail loudly if unset.
# Document every variable here (names only — never commit real values).

# Example — LLM/agent runtime configuration (uncomment and adjust):
# LLM_API_BASE=http://localhost:11434
# LLM_MODEL=
# LLM_API_KEY=
